SUMMARY:Deep Dives: An Olio House Party
DESCRIPTION:Tickets:This is a member celebration!&nbsp\; To attend this par
 ty you can sign up for our monthly membership which gives you 2 free event
 s each month. &nbsp\;You will then be able to invite one friend to the par
 ty &lt\;3&nbsp\;We're hosting a party built around obsessions\, deep dives
 \, and amateur passions.What are you obsessed with? What have you gone rea
 lly deep into — from childhood or adult life — that you don't get paid
  for?We'll spend the night giving a stage to our niche obsessions and cele
 brate each other for keeping curiosity alive! New friends\, miscellaneous 
 learnings\, deep convos and daaaaaaancing the night away.&nbsp\;What to ex
 pect:7:30pm: Come straight to the roof and upon arrival we will match you 
 with a group of friends based on our secret witchery8pm: You sit with your
  new friends and discuss a couple of curated prompts related to deep dives
  and obsessions.9pm: We'll enjoy 5\, 5-minute deep dives presented by Olio
  members. 10-11pm: DJ begins and we dance our asses offTake dance breaks t
 o check out the tri-folds and little demonstrations around the room to see
  what obsessions your friends have dove into.Enjoy a classic cereal bar to
  fuel your energy throughout the night1:30-2:30am: DJ Zimmy Dynamite winds
  down the evening with an ambient set. We'll stretch\, and have tea becaus
 e we love our bodiesTickets:This is a member celebration! To attend this p
 arty you can sign up for our monthly membership which gives you 2 free eve
 nts each month. &nbsp\;You will then be able to invite one friend to the p
 arty &lt\;3&nbsp\;What is Think Olio?Think Olio is an ongoing experiment i
 n lifelong learning. We are a community of open-minded people who gather t
 o exchange ideas with new friends and connect over art\, literature\, and 
 philosophy.An Olio is what we call the social learning events we’ve been
  organizing since 2015. A blend between a lecture and a house party\, Olio
 s are led by a teacher who loves sharing their passions and the room is fi
 lled with curious\, open-minded New Yorkers.&nbsp\;Eight months into creat
 ing a venue\, one of our favorite feelings has been the moments where we
 ’ve stepped outside of time. We’ve created a space where conversations
  don’t feel rushed\, people are greeted with hugs\, and as a community\,
  we spontaneously come up with new ideas (like the dial-up-disco house par
 ty) and bring them to life.Our goal is to spark new perspectives\, ignite 
 curiosity\, and enjoy ourselves socially—an alternative to typical night
 life options.Check out our full calendarDisclaimer: By purchasing a ticket
 \, you agree to have your photo/video used for social media/marketing mate
 rials. If you prefer to not have your photo taken\, feel free to send us a
  note.\n\nTickets & info: https://www.viewcy.com/event/deep_dives_an_olio_
 h
URL:https://www.viewcy.com/event/deep_dives_an_olio_h
